OL,3,CFather found guilty of murdering
OL,4,Cinfant son
OL,6,FA 29-year old Co Armagh man was handed
OL,7,Fa Life Sentence on Wednesday after he
OL,8,Fwas found guilty by a jury of
OL,9,Fmurdering his son.
OL,11,FAfter deliberating for over six hours,
OL,12,Fthe jury at Belfast Crown Court
OL,13,Fconvicted Craig Rowland of murdering
OL,14,Fhis son Lewis Oliver Rowland, who died
OL,15,Faged three in October 2018.
OL,17,FThe youngster sustained life-changing
OL,18,Fbrain injuries in November 2015 after
OL,19,Fbeing violently shaken by his father
OL,20,Fwhen he was aged 13 weeks old.
