OL,6,FRowland displayed no emotion as he
OL,7,Fstood in the dock of Belfast Crown
OL,8,FCourt when the guilty verdict - by a
OL,9,Fmajority of 11 to one - was delivered.
OL,11,FThe convicted child killer was then
OL,12,Faddressed by Mr Justice O'Hara, who
OL,13,Ftold him: "The jury has found you
OL,14,Fguilty of the murder of Lewis in
OL,15,FOctober 2018.
OL,17,F"As a result of the fact that you have
OL,18,Fbeen found guilty of murder, I must
OL,19,Fpass a sentence of Life Imprisonment
OL,20,Fon you.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
