OL,6,F"There will be a hearing as soon as
OL,7,Fpossible as to what the minimum time
OL,8,Fyou will spend in prison is before you
OL,9,Fare considered for release by the
OL,10,FParole Commissioners.
OL,12,F"I sentence you now to Life
OL,13,FImprisonment."
OL,15,FAfter this, Rowland nodded at the
OL,16,FJudge, who then thanked the jury their
OL,17,Fattention and service.
