OL,6,FSaying "this has not been an easy case
OL,7,Fto hear" as it involved "the killing
OL,8,Fof an infant", Mr Justice O'Hara told
OL,9,Fthem that information would be
OL,10,Fprovided to them if they required help
OL,11,For support.
OL,13,FHe added: "Now your role in this case
OL,14,Fis over. Thank you very much again for
OL,15,Fyour contribution and your dedication
OL,16,Fto this case. You are now free to go."
OL,18,FPre-sentence reports will now be
OL,19,Fcompiled on Rowland and the Judge set
OL,20,Fthe date for the Tariff hearing as
OL,21,FTuesday December 17.
