OL,6,FIn a trial that spanned over a period
OL,7,Fof four weeks, the jury heard that on
OL,8,FNovember 20, 2015, Craig Rowland and
OL,9,FLaura Graham brought their 13-week old
OL,10,Fson Lewis to Craigavon Area Hospital.
OL,12,FWhen the pair arrived at the hospital
OL,13,Fat around 1.30pm on November 20,
OL,14,Fmedics were told that the evening
OL,15,Fbefore, their son had been unsettled
OL,16,Fand unwell.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/15
