OL,6,FThey also said they had put Lewis in
OL,7,Fhis buggy and walked three miles from
OL,8,Ftheir home at Millington Park in
OL,9,FPortadown to the hospital, which took
OL,10,Faround an hour, and didn't call an
OL,11,Fambulance as they had no phone.
OL,13,FThe gravely ill baby underwent a CT
OL,14,FScan that revealed he had serious
OL,15,Fbrain injuries which resulted in a
OL,16,Fpermanent and severe disability.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/15
