OL,6,FFurther examinations of Lewis on that
OL,7,Fdate revealed he also had a spinal
OL,8,Finjury, a healing rib fracture and
OL,9,Fmultiple bruises on his neck, head and
OL,10,Fchest.
OL,12,FDue to the severity of his injuries,
OL,13,FLewis was rushed to the Royal Victoria
OL,14,FHospital for Sick Children in Belfast
OL,15,Fthat afternoon suffering from a bleed
OL,16,Fto his brain.
OL,18,FThe jury heard evidence from a nurse
OL,19,Fwho was on duty in the Intensive Care
OL,20,FUnit and who recalled Lewis being
OL,21,Ftaken into theatre at around 9pm.
