OL,6,FShe was asked by Crown barrister David
OL,7,FRussell KC about a conversation she
OL,8,Fhad with the baby's parents regarding
OL,9,Ftheir baby son and concerns he might
OL,10,Fnot survive the night.
OL,12,FThe nurse said she told Rowland and
OL,13,FGraham that a room in the hospital has
OL,14,Fbeen prepared for them to stay
OL,15,Fovernight, but that they declined this
OL,16,Foffer and said they were going home.
