OL,6,FThe jury also heard that after being
OL,7,Freleased from the Royal Hospital,
OL,8,FLewis was taken into foster care. He
OL,9,Fcouldn't walk or talk and had to be
OL,10,Ffed through a nasal tube, but he could
OL,11,Fsmile at his foster parents.
OL,13,FIn July 2018, consideration was given
OL,14,Fregarding a longer-term feeding tube
OL,15,Fand in October 2018 the little boy
OL,16,Funderwent surgery in a paediatric
OL,17,Fintensive care unit to insert a
OL,18,Ffeeding tube directly into his stomach.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/15
