OL,6,FThe surgery was conducted on October
OL,7,F4, 2018 and he had further surgery on
OL,8,FOctober 17 and 19 to re-adjust the
OL,9,Ffeeding tube.
OL,11,FIn the early hours of October 20,
OL,12,FLewis developed breathing difficulties
OL,13,Fand a chest X-Ray indicated he had
OL,14,Fpneumonia. He passed away later that
OL,15,Fday, at 1.30pm, aged three.
