OL,15,FSentence was imposed, Rowland was
OL,16,Fhandcuffed by prison staff.
OL,18,FAs he was being removed from the dock
OL,19,Fand led into custody, he again shouted
OL,20,Fand said "you are all corrupt, there
OL,21,Fwas no evidence."
